{"tid":303020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［打臉支那］習總訪港慶回歸 美國就宣布對台售武贈慶","createTime":"2017-06-29T23:48:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-30T00:52:56.000Z","uid":41351,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"38207d364480e79326fc558e71204e9607c8cfa6","tid":303020,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T23:48:34.000Z","msg":"（中央社記者黃兆平紐約29日專電）「華爾街日報」報導，川普政府今天知會國會已批准售予台灣價值約14億2000萬美元的軍備案。這是川普執政以來，首批對台軍售案。<br />\n<br />\n川普當選後執行其所謂美國的「一中」政策，有別於前任政府。美國務院宣布軍售案時間，選在巴拿馬剛與中國建交不久，以及中國大陸國家主席習近平刻在香港訪問，即將主持新任行政長官就職典禮前夕。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院發言人諾爾特（Heather Nauert）指出，國務院已知會國會數筆軍購案，此舉意在強化美國支持台灣的防衛能力。<br />\n<br />\n美國國會可在30天內決定批准或否決軍購案。報導說，美方此舉勢必激怒中國。<br />\n<br />\n不過，報導引述諾爾特指出，「我們（美方）長期以來的『一個中國』政策沒有改變。」也即美過去近40年來承認與中國大陸外交關係，而非台灣。「紐約時報」也引用路透社及美聯社作同樣報導。<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201706300021.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F201706300021.aspx&d=Lef6mzCXcJ9AA5ymDh00qG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=aacd6f52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201706300021.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"572838c7e4eb035e16c301f0989ebabc643ed0d8","tid":303020,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T00:38:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19bebb2f65c5f5c8c129ab2a05ef40c1c32a86e7","tid":303020,"uid":12591,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T00:44:38.000Z","msg":"一個中國 一個台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbfbbc974b0c6044362a407ec709d668d472e4e8","tid":303020,"uid":27458,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T00:51:59.000Z","msg":"賣定唔賣嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eba6a6368836b01d67d537ed846840c448ed6c3","tid":303020,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T00:52:56.000Z","msg":"當你以為侵侵一心諗住奶共，我無諗過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> good job<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}